    _DISABLE Sendmail_
1. vi /etc/rc.conf

# sendmail_flags="-L sm-mta -C/etc/mail/localhost.cf -bd -q30m" #comment out this line
sendmail_flags=NO  # add this line to disable sendmail from starting at boot time

2. crontab -e

Look for the lines that look like this and remove them or comment them out with a#

# sendmail clientmqueue runner
# */30 * * * * /usr/sbin/sendmail -L sm-msp-queue -Ac -q # add a "#" to comment it out
